        <div n="Y09C27L3">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">By <hi rend="italics">Dean</hi> S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C27L3-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>E People of <hi rend="italics">Ireland</hi> both Country and City,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-2" n="2">Come listen with Patience, and hear out my Ditty,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-3" n="3">At this Time I'll chuse to be wiser than witty.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-4" n="4">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which no Body can deny</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-5" n="5"><lb/>The Half-pence are coming, the Nation's undoing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-6" n="6">There's an End of your Ploughing, and Baking, and Brewing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-7" n="7">In short you must all go to Rack and to Ruin.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-8" n="8">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-9" n="9"><lb/>Both high Men and low Men, and thick Men and tall Men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-10" n="10">And rich Men and poor Men, and free Men and thrall Men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-11" n="11">Will suffer, and this Man, and that Man, and all Men.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-12" n="12">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-13" n="13"><lb/>The Soldier is ruin'd, poor Man, by his Pay,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-14" n="14">His five Pence will prove but a Farthing a Day,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-15" n="15">For Meat, or for Drink, or he must run away.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-16" n="16">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-17" n="17"><lb/>When he pulls out his two Pence, the Tapster says not,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-18" n="18">That ten times as much he must pay for his Shot,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-19" n="19">And thus the poor Soldier he must go to Pot.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-20" n="20">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-21" n="21"><lb/>If he goes to the Baker, the Baker will huff,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-22" n="22">And twenty Pence have for a two Penny Loaf,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-23" n="23">Then, Dog, Rogue, and Rascal, and so kick and cuff.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-24" n="24">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-25" n="25"><lb/>Again, to the Market whenever he goes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-26" n="26">The Butcher and Soldier must be mortal Foes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-27" n="27">One cuts off an Ear, and the other a Nose.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-28" n="28">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-29" n="29"><lb/>The Butcher is stout, and he values no Swagger,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-30" n="30">A Cleaver's a Match any Time for a Dagger,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-31" n="31">And a blue Sleeve may give such a Cuff as may stagger.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-32" n="32">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-33" n="33"><lb/>The Beggars themselves will be broke in a trice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-34" n="34">When thus their poor Farthings are sunk in their Price,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-35" n="35">When nothing is left they must live on their Lice.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-36" n="36">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-37" n="37"><lb/>The 'Squire who's got him twelve thousand a Year,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-38" n="38">O Lord! what a Mountain his Rents would appear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-39" n="39">Shou'd he take 'em, he would not have House-Room I fear.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-40" n="40">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-41" n="41"><lb/>Tho' at present he lives in a very large House,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-42" n="42">There would not be Room in it left for a Mouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-43" n="43">But the 'Squire's too wise, he won't take a Souse.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-44" n="44">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-45" n="45"><lb/>The Farmer who comes with his Rent in this Cash,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-46" n="46">For taking these Counters, and being so rash,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-47" n="47">Will be kick'd out of Doors, both himself and his Trash.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-48" n="48">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-49" n="49"><lb/>For in all the Leases that ever we hold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-50" n="50">We must pay our Rent in good Silver and Gold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-51" n="51">And not in brass Tokens of such a base Mould.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-52" n="52">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-53" n="53"><lb/>The wisest of Lawyers all swear they will warrant</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-54" n="54">No Money but Silver and Gold can be current,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-55" n="55">And since they will swear it, we all may be sure on't.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-56" n="56">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-57" n="57"><lb/>And I think after all it would be very strange,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-58" n="58">To give current Money for base in Exchange,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-59" n="59">Like a fine Lady swapping her Moles for the Mange.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-60" n="60">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-61" n="61"><lb/>But read the King's Patent, and there you will find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-62" n="62">That no Man need take 'em but who has a Mind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-63" n="63">For which we must say his Majesty's kind.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-64" n="64">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-65" n="65"><lb/>Now God bless the Draper who open'd our Eyes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-66" n="66">I'm sure by his Book that the Writer is wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-67" n="67">He shews us the Cheat from the End to the Rise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-68" n="68">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-69" n="69"><lb/>Nay, farther he shews it a very hard Case,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-70" n="70">That this Fellow <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi>'s of a very Bad Race,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-71" n="71">Should of all the fine Gentry of <hi rend="italics">Ireland</hi> take Place</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-72" n="72">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-73" n="73"><lb/>That he and his Half-pence should come to weigh down</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-74" n="74">Our Subjects so loyal and true to the Crown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-75" n="75">But I hope after all that they will be his own.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-76" n="76">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-77" n="77"><lb/>This Book I do tell you is writ for your Goods,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-78" n="78">And a very Good Book against Mr. <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi>'s,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-79" n="79">If you stand true together, he's left in the Suds.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-80" n="80">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-81" n="81"><lb/>Ye Shop-Men and Trades-Men and Farmers go read it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-82" n="82">For I think in my Soul at this time that you need it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-83" n="83">Or I Gad if you don't there's an End of your Credit.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C27L3-line-84" n="84">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which no Body can deny</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
